      "body": "Hello SecureTech Solutions Team,\n\nWe are ready to move forward with the installation of the AeroSecure biometric scanners at Heathrow International Terminal and would like to coordinate the on-site work with your team.\n\nProject Overview\n• Hardware: BioScan Technologies biometric scanners (model BS-X200)\n• Location: Security checkpoints A12–A18, Terminal 5, Heathrow International Airport\n• Schedule: Target window 14–17 July 2025 (flexible by ±2 days if needed)\n• Network: Ethernet (PoE), VLAN 52, static IP range 10.32.44.200–10.32.44.230\n• Electrical: 48 V PoE, 0.8 A per unit\n• System Integration: New scanner IDs must be registered in the AeroSecure access-control system immediately after physical installation.\n\nAction Items for SecureTech\n1. Confirm your team’s availability for the dates above.\n2. Review the attached technical specification sheet (PDF link below) and advise if any additional materials or cabling are required.\n3. Provide a list of on-site engineers so that temporary access badges can be issued in advance.\n\nResources\nTechnical Specifications: https://www.notion.so/Biometric-Scanner-Technical-Specifications-1f00dc8fa0db817094fecdb75b667234 \nInstallation Guide: (internal link provided separately to authorized personnel)\n\nSecurity Note\nInitial administrative credentials will be supplied onsite to authorized staff only. Please ensure that passwords are rotated immediately after commissioning.\n\nPlease acknowledge receipt of this message and let us know if the proposed schedule works for you. We look forward to working together on a smooth deployment.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Title]\n[Company]\n"
